title: Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured
text:
> Top News Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured Georgia wide receiver Reggie Davis (81) can't make the catch during the second half of an NCAA college football game against Tennessee Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 in Knoxville, Tenn. Tennessee won 38-31. (AP Photo/Wade Payne) Search Help
